@startuml
title MazarbuLib - System Context

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Embedded Application" as App
actor "UART RX Source\n(ISR / callback / serial input)" as Rx
actor "UART TX Sink\n(terminal / serial monitor)" as Tx

rectangle "MazarbuLib\nPortable C99 UART table rendering library" as Lib {
  component "Public API\ninclude/mazarbulib.h" as API
  component "Core Implementation\nsrc/mazarbulib.c" as Core
  component "Compile-time Config\ninclude/mazarbulib_config.h" as Config
}

rectangle "Platform Adapter Code\n(user supplied)" as Platform {
  component "uart_send(data,len)" as UartSend
  component "screen_clear()" as ScreenClear
}

App --> API : init/register/tick
Rx --> API : feed received char
API --> Core : API calls
Config --> API : macro limits
Config --> Core : macro limits
Core --> UartSend : transmit rendered output
Core --> ScreenClear : optional clear before redraw
UartSend --> Tx : UART bytes

note right of Lib
Single-threaded, static allocation only,
no malloc, no OS dependencies,
one translation unit.
end note

@enduml
